{"tid":326213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【後續行動】長毛：總辭　搞新政府？　市民：係　自主派更可先建立臨立局","createTime":"2017-07-17T20:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T20:21:46.000Z","uid":47714,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19d09bde651133110e270b7b4e4917e825774742","tid":326213,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T20:57:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1050754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1050754&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=01c6e9b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1050754&h=41dfd2e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1050754</a><br />\n<br />\n【總辭不總辭？】長毛：係咪另搞新政府，唔交税唔守所有法例？<br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）四名立法會議員遭政府入稟司法覆核取消議員資格，非建制派議員數目減至24席。韓連山昨日均提出民主派議員應總辭，稱總辭會是「震撼的舉措」。社民連梁國雄直斥，呼籲總辭的人是「搵笨」，指是等同「與政府正式決裂」，更反問：「係咪永遠唔返黎，搞一個新嘅香港人民政府先？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/fanwa.kaoka/posts/460973784275498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffanwa.kaoka%2Fposts%2F460973784275498&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=76b4e74b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/fanwa.kaoka/posts/460973784275498</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Fanwa Kaoka<br />\n<br />\n法國大革命由議會失效為起點，「第三階級」近600位議員被禁止進入議廳。但佢哋並冇任何一刻諗過總辭，而係以議員身份，將「第三階級」改稱「國民議會」，然後自行去網球場開會。<br />\n<br />\nBilly Wong:<br />\n至於總辭有冇用就類似破釜沉舟有冇用，我就唔識評價喇<br />\n<br />\nLittPi Chan:<br />\n霸左維園佢，黎個維園宣言<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/desjacobins/posts/543317099125365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdesjacobins%2Fposts%2F543317099125365&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=96458d20\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/desjacobins/posts/543317099125365</a><br />\n<br />\n劉仲敬2014年11月：<br />\n//民選議員如果有立陶宛人的智慧和決斷，就能實現制憲會議和中聯辦兩個政權並立的局面。如果蘇軍一如既往地畏懼國際體系，寧願派地下黨和黑社會襲擊制憲會議；後者就能自然行使戰爭權利，截留各官署和納稅集團的支持。只要雙頭政權長期僵持，香港就勝利了。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/groups/glory.nx.forum/permalink/269079320236416/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fglory.nx.forum%2Fpermalink%2F269079320236416%2F&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d91852f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/groups/glory.nx.forum/permalink/269079320236416/</a><br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n總辭後有後續才有意義，例如成立新政府，對不交舊政府稅的市民，新政府出辦法保護。<br />\n<br />\n西藏僧人自焚，如果沒有達賴，就真的只是自焚。總辭是可以自滅的，沒有後續更大對抗計劃，就只是盡地一煲博意外發展。<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n我用詞上由「有辦法」改為「出辦法」。其實就如雨傘革命的情況，得道多助，展示出意志，真正要帶來改變、解決問題，公眾見到政治人物向出路行，就會幫忙，甚至加入。"},{"pid":"1ce7909ffe3a712e853b5cc1e26fc0e580a3faff","tid":326213,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T20:58:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/07/曾焯文：dq議員　廣場制憲？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F07%2F%E6%9B%BE%E7%84%AF%E6%96%87%EF%BC%9Adq%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E3%80%80%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E5%88%B6%E6%86%B2%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d6680839\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/07/曾焯文：dq議員　廣場制憲？/</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：曾焯文<br />\n<br />\n兵臨城下，民主派議員若真心為港，並且想長遠自保，則唯有兵行險著，從以下二途擇一。第一，佔領垃圾會，領導市民抗爭（網民建議）。第二，民主派議員總辭，後著係廣場制憲，成立影子政府，宣布立法會為非法議會，港共為非法政府，事關行政與司法立法合作，迫害民選異見議員，（行政當局及立會建制派又協助中共殖民香港；濫捕濫告社運人士等）。由於民主派議員多由直選產生，有公民授權，其所組成的影子政府有民意基礎，富公信力，必能得到多數香港市民及國際社會支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/raymond.yukman/posts/1521465074586190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fraymond.yukman%2Fposts%2F1521465074586190&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=72c15ef6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/raymond.yukman/posts/1521465074586190</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：黃毓民<br />\n<br />\n港共政權夥同司法機關<br />\n<br />\n公然禠奪民意代表議席<br />\n<br />\n泛民必須總辭公投自決<br />\n<br />\n#沒有人是孤島 喪鐘為你我而敲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/chengchungtai/posts/793941474113545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchengchungtai%2Fposts%2F793941474113545&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d180529a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/chengchungtai/posts/793941474113545</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n<br />\n「總辭」使非建制派「大和解」，全部同一陣線尋求國際壓力，請求美國利用並修改「香港關係法」與中共攤牌吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/civicpassionpage/posts/1865844287010162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivicpassionpage%2Fposts%2F1865844287010162&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=10744529\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/civicpassionpage/posts/1865844287010162</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：熱血公民<br />\n<br />\n【集體總辭匯聚民意壓力 遊說各國停止姑息中共】<br />\n&mdash;熱血公民回應宣誓覆核案判決聲明<br />\n<br />\n高等法院今日裁定，劉小麗、梁國雄、羅冠聰及姚松炎的立法會議員就職宣誓無效，議員資格會被撤銷。判決的依據是按照二○一六年十一月中共人大常委會對《基本法》第104條釋法，北京的橡皮圖章人大常委會聯同香港的傀儡政權，一起架空了立法機關。<br />\n<br />\n立法會《議事規則》第49B.條列明，除了議員本人被判處監禁一個月以上，要取消議員的資格就須獲得出席會議的議員的三分之二多數票，通過譴責動議。此一罷免機制，是由議事堂內的民意代表，決定涉事民意代表的去留，其精神是尊重民意。如今北京干預香港立法機關，特區政府「行政干預立法」，變相剝奪了香港選民的投票權，使香港成為極權社會。<br />\n<br />\n分組點票的防線已經失守，議會抗爭亦已走到盡頭。各位非建制議員理應總辭，匯聚民意壓力，並遊說自由世界諸國終結對中華人民共和國的姑息政策，甚至呼籲美國檢討《美國－香港政策法》，重新審視香港是否一個在政治、經濟、貿易政策方面與中國大陸完全不同的地區。<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民主席<br />\n鄭松泰<br />\n二○一七年七月十四日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155417539477225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155417539477225&d=d0aqck87GLUge5rEorWbkZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5949e3d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155417539477225</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：陳雲<br />\n<br />\n一、泛民議員宣布總體辭職，但杯葛補選（因為補選條例令他們無法自身參選），令香港立法會懸空，形成憲制危機。<br />\n<br />\n二、泛民連同被取消議席的港獨自決派議員，搭飛機集體去美國和歐盟遊說，尋求國際社會介入香港。得不到答覆，部分就留在華盛頓或紐約紮營抗議。<br />\n<br />\n三、泛民港獨自決派搭飛機返回香港，在香港舉行無限期的市區佔領，令國際干預進入香港，必要時在韓戰爆發期間在美國領事監護之下廣場制憲，成立香港共和國。"},{"pid":"80431b7822b215c1fec7cd716e4d183a08fa3e70","tid":326213,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcea9a41938585beaafdd3233c81f596f88e07ce","tid":326213,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:51:08.000Z","msg":"仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f937d6517ae03d862e0d6563bb4075d282a4c6f","tid":326213,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86a7bc8a60346281057da11dc901c119ea996052","tid":326213,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打官司打第一單案例就打得過嘅"},{"pid":"55a383c53108ebaa61c7a0d27c17ab82c252ea3a","tid":326213,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打官司打第一單案例就打得過嘅</blockquote><br />\n梁遊一早做緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8847ca0e17500f94687e6de31da29b8be6e94142","tid":326213,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打官司打第一單案例就打得過嘅</blockquote><br />\n梁遊一早做緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泛民先前恥笑同怪緊佢哋㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2862c926f34b10a06dc1a3d8f6c0c8a17fde5c6c","tid":326213,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"304368814cc0650c772bea6a8723eb4a37785cf7","tid":326213,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點成立?  起碼都要做到太陽花咁樣先有可能成立到</blockquote><br />\n所以可由自決派mix本土/獨派 做起先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要有行動力<br />\n不需大，只需精巧而緊密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e251b4513a96110254fb67c3b11b07e8524db646","tid":326213,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58104f681b2509db64a9a3abed25cae49caf34bf","tid":326213,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee82d53ed91a313b468b8e7f079884aea4ada6c7","tid":326213,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點成立?  起碼都要做到太陽花咁樣先有可能成立到</blockquote><br />\n所以可由自決派mix本土/獨派 做起先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要有行動力<br />\n不需大，只需精巧而緊密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題又黎, 就係錢同資源</blockquote><br />\n打官司既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f72daa16f73710ea2ad7a69037c0601e7e0c38","tid":326213,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉反對黨都識玩過犯民"},{"pid":"1d3b31c9237afc058df7b1ca8d3e8a12dc6b9bc3","tid":326213,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"51c5fa87b9970572ce9e8b15b12f3c685579adc3","tid":326213,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作者：Fanwa Kaoka<br />\n<br />\n法國大革命由議會失效為起點，「第三階級」近600位議員被禁止進入議廳。但佢哋並冇任何一刻諗過總辭，而係以議員身份，將「第三階級」改稱「國民議會」，然後自行去網球場開會。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國大革命無用「總辭」呢隻字, 因為「總辭」係近代既TERM<br />\n<br />\n法國大革命另立國民議會, 已經無打算行駛原本議會既議員職能<br />\n性質同總辭原本議會係無分別<br />\n<br />\n國民議會就係另起爐灶, 推翻既有議會, 係革命<br />\n網球場會議唔係吹下水架, 係真革命架<br />\n<br />\n咁請問, 係咪準備革命先？"},{"pid":"abcfa6f06c32c70a1bf05d171d644de55f5f5c27","tid":326213,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲拎錢黎打官司？<br />\n不如拎黎成立國民議會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打官司打第一單案例就打得過嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你另立議會, 就係革命<br />\n<br />\n革命就係全面推翻政權, 連原本既法院都推翻<br />\n<br />\n法官係送去斷頭台<br />\n<br />\n仲打乜撚官司？<br />\n<br />\n自己都唔知自己做緊乜"},{"pid":"3bb8d04a86c5cd4c6d0889c80c4b83da118e66a7","tid":326213,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:08:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最理想既 scenario 就係天琦,浩天,陳國強等人被DQ既時候搞一個類似太陽花咁既示威</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後被黑警打柒?<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀, 法國大革命國民議會, <br />\n<br />\n人地法國佬係有武裝力量做後盾, 先可以同法王政府分庭抗禮架"},{"pid":"f523cd25fee338808b255c79376459b71cf0493a","tid":326213,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最理想既 scenario 就係天琦,浩天,陳國強等人被DQ既時候搞一個類似太陽花咁既示威</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後被黑警打柒?<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀, 法國大革命國民議會, <br />\n<br />\n人地法國佬係有武裝力量做後盾, 先可以同法王政府分庭抗禮架</blockquote><br />\n等美軍幾時有艦再黎香港補給<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果時去做野係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d236ca76323ae7afac5b522f428679907d34f057","tid":326213,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"啲五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個post冇撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}